<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب ل د:</span> <span class="c2">(الْبَلَدُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الْبَلْدَةُ)</span> بِمَعْنًى وَالْجَمْعُ <span class="c2">(بِلَادٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(بُلْدَانٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الْبَلَادَةُ)</span> بِالْفَتْحِ ضِدُّ الذَّكَاءِ وَبَابُهُ ظَرُفَ فَهُوَ بَلِيدٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>